Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,およそ遠しとされしもの　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:12.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見慣れた動植物とは　まるで違うと　おぼしきモノ達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヒトは古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:16.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父は酔うと　よくこんな話をした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何年前になるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:25.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ある晩　隣の村から帰る途中で道に迷ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,散々歩き回るも　とうとう道すらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,困り果てていると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:42.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人だ　助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あっちに道が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　あの灯りは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:07.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,近づくと　得も言われぬ酒の馨しい匂いが漂ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そのうち一口　その酒を飲んでみたくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっそりと宴の中に紛れ込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その酒は黄金色の光を帯びていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,禄助　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:48.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ご苦労だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前も今日は　家に戻ってのんびりするといい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの　蔵元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今年の酒　少しばかり持って帰りたいのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　いいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:14.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今年のできなら　親父さんもお前の酒を認めてくれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,子どもの頃　よくこうして　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:34.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父の作った酒を　隣の村まで届けに行ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:41.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな時　山道に入ると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも何かに纏わり付かれるような気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あぶねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:05:00.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　やっとの思いで使い先へ着いた頃には
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,明らかに酒の量が減ってしまっているのだった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:11.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの時　それを蔵元に告げられ　私はひどく叱られたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父は　それを咎めようとはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　山で何かに絡まれたか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだか目に見えないものがずっと周りにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:31.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それで　気が付いたら酒が減ってて　本当だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:38.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　あれらは　旨い酒が好物なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:42.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうやら　今年の酒も気に入ってくれたようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　まだまだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの酒に比べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前にも話したことがあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「光る酒」だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの味が今でも忘れられんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんはずっとあれを目指してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酒は生き物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,感覚を全部使って　言葉のすべてを聞き取れれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いずれはきっと答えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:28.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　お前も跡を継ぐ気なら　それをよーく覚えておきな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ついにできたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:42.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,旨い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだか足が縺れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酔っちまったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　ここ　どこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どっかで道を間違えたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻るか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だこりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,けものの毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,待て　こら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこ行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このっ　返せっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　あの灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな所で　一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何してんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　その…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　光酒持ってんじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　遠慮することはねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光る酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:43.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃ　これは　父さんの言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見ねえ顔だな　新参蟲師か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酒をやれば　離れるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師…この人らが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よぉ　ギンコ　蟲煙草のいいのがあるぞ　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,へえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒と交換でどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ　切らしちまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺ももうほとんど残っていねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,頼む　一滴でいいからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　そのタバコ全部となら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒切らしたあんたが悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　そう言うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そう　あんただよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そん中　光酒だろう　ちょっとばかし分けてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,随分重そうじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ケチケチすんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,タバコがいらねんなら　他にもいろいろあるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この盃　どこかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:31.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんでも名のある器だそうでな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昔　光酒一杯と交換してやったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　兄ちゃんお目が高い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:41.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その後　売りに行ったら　ガラクタ同然と言われたわけだが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,てーめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.95,TXT JP (O-UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ギンコ　余計なこと言うんじゃねえよ　このっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんだ　これは父さんがいつも持ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　人の商売邪魔していいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これをもらえるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒とそれ　変えてくれんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　まあ　構わねえが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,飲まないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:09.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういえば　誰もあの光る酒を飲んではいない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体　あの酒は何のために…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　遅いな　ワタリの連中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何やら　準備に手間取っているようだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,またか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちっと様子見てくるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺も…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄ちゃん　光酒　たんまり持ってんね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺にも分けてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,わしもわしも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イサザ　俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:56.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,達者にしてたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:58.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おかげさんで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じき始めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:05.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今　場所が定まったところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光脈のへそが　また見つけにくくなってんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:15.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　ここも古い光脈だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:20.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,次からは　別の光脈から分けてもらったほうがよさそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,寿命か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,地中深くにもぐるだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,きっとまた　力を蓄えたら戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:45.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何が始まるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光る酒が増えた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体どういうからくりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　おかしいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしや　偽物か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…違う　俺じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ　あいつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつから買ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,偽物持ち込んだのはあいつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　待って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:27.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,捕まえろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺なんか　まずいことしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,速く山を降りよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　こっち
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,悪気はなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:03.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺はただ　あんたらの光る酒を飲んでみたくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,同業のふりして紛れ込んだのは謝る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:07.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　虫師じゃねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:15.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　俺は麓の郷の蔵人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,蔵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　その酒は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今年　うちのくらで造った酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:27.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何年も　試行錯誤して　ようやくできた酒なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,病で臥せってる父に飲ませてやりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,持って帰る途中　道に迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,紛れ込んちまっただけなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どうか見逃してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体　どうやって造った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,杜氏だった父が倒れてから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うちのくらの酒はすっかり味が落ちてしまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父のいう通りに　やってるつもりだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうすぐに　父の経験に追いつけるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それでも　くらの名を落としたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,米を変え　水を変え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,手を尽くしたが無駄だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:14.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だがある時　ふと　酵母を換えるとどうなるかと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うちではずっとくらにいる酵母を使ってきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,野生のもので試してみようと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酵母は糖分を好むため
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花の蜜にいる酵母を集めて歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それらを増やして使ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほとんどは大した変化は見られなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:40.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　たっだ一つの樽だけが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,黄金色に輝く　美酒となった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花の蜜から？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その酒　飲んでも異常なかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,少量じゃわからなかったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと妙な酔い方をしたな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,赤黒い毛の幻覚を見えたり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃ幻覚じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,猩々の髭って虫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,虫師が講を行う時の案内に使う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酒を好む虫は多いが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やつらは光酒だけを巣に持って帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やつらまで騙されたわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいだろう　あんたの話　信じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見逃してくれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:34.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その代わり　その酒を世に出すのはやめてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酔うと虫が見える酒なんざ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,出回ったらいろいろ無駄な騒ぎになりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それにいくら味がよくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:50.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,幻が見えるんじゃ　あんたらにとってもいい評判にはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おそらく　あんたが酵母の代わりに使ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,吸蜜糖って虫だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酵母と同様　糖を食って酒とする微細な虫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒偽造の原料として用いるという説はあると
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,成功した例はいまだ聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたの蔵人としての技量は確かってことだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:23.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,聞いていいか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:27.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの光酒　とは一体　なんなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,生命そのものの姿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,虫わずらいには万薬の長だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,虫とは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　世を構成してるものの一部さね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それ以上でも　以下でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ところで　あんたの造った酒な
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,世に出せないってのは表向きにって話ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,翌朝　くらへ引き返すと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:13.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,酒に酔った蔵人たちや蔵本が幻覚を見たと騒ぎになっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,話し合った結果　その酒の出荷は取りやめとなり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,当面　奥のくらにおいておくことにした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,というのも　時折妙な客が訪れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:30.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その酒を買っていくようになったためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:36.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの人ら　一体どこであの酒の話　聞きつけてきてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,表向きにはって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺らにとっちゃ使える酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,噂流しといてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おもしろい酒造るくらがあるってな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことしたらあいつら　捕まえにくんじゃないか　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただ売るだけなら問題ねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さっきは光酒として取引したのはまずかったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,要は　使え用だ
